data.name: label12.Text
data.value:
Define the discovary domain by specifying ip address ranges to be included or excluded from discovery. Whenver a new neighbor discovered, its CDP reported ip address will be compared to these lists whether to include that neighbor in discovery or not. An empty include list allows any host be discovered so does an empty exclusion list.
Even if an ip range is explicitly set for exclusion a host in that network can still be added to discovery list manually on the first page.
